edu.subram43purdue.travelplanner

Class Vacation

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.subram43purdue.travelplanner.Vacation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Vacation
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class represents a vacation, which has 5 different fields/attributes: a name, location, start date, end date, and an array list of events. This class implements the Serializable interface, so that it can be written to external storage using java's object output stream capabilities
